&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coordinate Marketplace Fit:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner closely with Employer-side product teams to ensure a healthy, balanced marketplace where seeker actions lead to successful hires.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead &amp;amp; Mentor:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage and grow a high-performing team of Product Managers, fostering a culture of ownership and excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as an Owner:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full accountability for your product domain, from high-level KPI setting to the nuances of daily execution.&lt;/li&gt;
